#: _inc/lib/debugger/class-jetpack-cxn-tests.php:763
msgid "Jetpack Sync has been disabled on your site. This could be impacting some of your site’s Jetpack-powered features. Developers may enable / disable syncing using the Sync Settings API."
msgstr "Jetpack Sync ຖືກປິດການໃຊ້ງານໃນເວັບໄຊຂອງທ່ານ. ສິ່ງນີ້ອາດສົ່ງຜົນກະທົບຕໍ່ບາງຄຸນສົມບັດຂອງ Jetpack. ນັກພັດທະນາສາມາດເປີດ / ປິດການຊິ້ງຂໍ້ມູນໂດຍໃຊ້ Sync Settings API."

